data.description: Take another peek at all of room this home has to offer, inside and out. This charming all-brick home is situated on 3 acres of serene countryside just outside of Delavan.  Taking a peek inside this over 3,000 square foot ranch, you are greeted with an open floor plan that starts with a well-appointed kitchen featuring granite countertops, all stainless steel appliances, kettle faucet, and a huge island with breakfast bar.  The connected dining room space features large windows offering breathtaking views of the surrounding farm fields.  Staying connected to the main living area is a large family room with gas fireplace. Down the hall is the formal living room, and full guest bathroom with new shower surround.  The appropriately sized main-level primary suite offers dual closets, and full bathroom with dual vanities and jacuzzi tub/shower.  Two additional large bedrooms give plenty of living space.  The laundry room features the third full bathroom. The basement level of the home features another large family room privileged with an in-floor heating system, as well as two additional flex spaces awaiting your finishing touches.  An abundance of outdoor areas and space await you, with a large freshly painted deck off the side of the home, and a large patio in the fenced-in backyard.  As if the two car garage wasn't enough, a standout feature of this property is the detached 60x53 machine shed, which offers endless possibilities for use, whether used as a workshop, a hobby space, or extra storage for your vehicles or recreational equipment, this versatile structure provides the flexibility you need to suit your lifestyle.  Updates to the home include roof in *2007*, Furnace and A/C in *2014*, kitchen remodel in *2014*, water filtration system installed in *2020*, new faucets in bathrooms, well system including pump, tank, piping, and other mechanical components all replaced 5 years ago, and new electric water heater in *2016*.  Fireplace, in-floor heating system, water softener all sold as-is. Make this home yours today!
